# Ligas de Tênis Design System — License

## 1. Design system code and documentation

The design system package (tokens, component reference code, guidelines, preview
HTML, scripts, and documentation) is part of the Venture Builder Workflow
developed by [Lucas Mattos](https://github.com/luccmattos).

**Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International
(CC BY-NC-ND 4.0)**

You may share the design system code and docs with attribution, for
non-commercial purposes, without creating adapted versions — per the full
license terms at https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/

## 2. Brand assets (logos, badges, product marks)

Files under `assets/` are **proprietary to Ligas de Tênis** and its leagues
(LAT, LISP, LIRJ, LT, LAS, LARB, and related products).

- Do not redistribute outside authorized league products and marketing.
- Do not modify logo artwork without brand-owner approval.
- Use only in contexts that represent Ligas de Tênis or its official leagues.

## 3. Fonts

Bebas Neue and Outfit are loaded from Google Fonts. Follow Google Fonts terms
for web usage. Self-hosting requires separate font license verification.

## 4. Third-party runtime (preview / UI kits)

Preview and UI kit pages load React and Babel from public CDNs (unpkg). Those
libraries are subject to their own licenses (MIT).
